Template: mozillavpn/ppa-deprecation-warning
Type: note
Description: Mozilla VPN PPA replaced by packages.mozilla.org
 The Mozilla VPN PPA source has been disabled and replaced with the
 packages.mozilla.org repository, which provides Mozilla VPN and other
 Mozilla products from a single source.
 .
 The original PPA source file has been saved with a .save extension and
 can be safely removed.

